00:33.701 --> 00:35.076
You don't want to watch

00:33.701 --> 00:35.076
a lingerie calendar shoot

00:35.118 --> 00:36.286
with your dad.

00:36.328 --> 00:37.454
And Alexandra likes...

00:37.496 --> 00:41.082
