11:15.800 --> 11:19.346
It will be a beautiful,

11:15.800 --> 11:19.346
romantic, magical evening

11:19.387 --> 11:21.598
that we need very badly,

11:21.640 --> 11:23.724
and nothing

11:21.640 --> 11:23.724
is going to derail it

11:23.766 --> 11:25.684
on penalty of death.

11:26.936 --> 11:28.480
Good.

11:30.357 --> 11:31.941
Do you want your army man?

11:34.194 --> 11:35.778
Okay.

11:35.820 --> 11:37.531
So, how's he doing?

11:37.572 --> 11:39.199
I was up with

11:37.572 --> 11:39.199
him all night.

