Why can't I just die?

11:47.582 --> 11:48.833
Stop talking

11:47.582 --> 11:48.833
like that, sir.

11:48.875 --> 11:51.628
This is just

11:48.875 --> 11:51.628
a momentary setback.

11:51.670 --> 11:54.005
I have nothing to live for.

11:54.047 --> 11:56.633
Mother no longer

11:54.047 --> 11:56.633
acknowledges me.

11:56.675 --> 11:58.843
I have no friends, no money.

11:58.885 --> 12:03.640
