11:58.885 --> 12:03.640
for my journey up here.

12:03.682 --> 12:05.808
If it means anything

12:03.682 --> 12:05.808
to you, sir,

12:05.850 --> 12:08.019
you taught me

12:05.850 --> 12:08.019
how to be a man.

12:08.061 --> 12:11.272
I have no idea

12:08.061 --> 12:11.272
who you are.

12:11.314 --> 12:12.691
You don't remember me?

12:12.731 --> 12:13.858
After all that

12:12.731 --> 12:13.858
time at Marlin,

12:13.900 --> 12:15.776
the hell that you

12:13.900 --> 12:15.776
put me through,

12:15.818 --> 12:17.445
you don't even

12:15.818 --> 12:17.445
remember me?

12:18.613 --> 12:20.990
Cadet Dudley?

12:21.032 --> 12:23.076
No! Eric!

12:23.117 --> 12:25.579
I just spent the last

12:23.117 --> 12:25.579
ten hours cradling you!

12:25.620 --> 12:28.164
Sir, this is because

12:25.620 --> 12:28.164
you're not feeling useful.

12:28.206 --> 12:29.957
Look, I've talked

12:28.206 --> 12:29.957
to some people

12:29.999 --> 12:32.252
