12:29.999 --> 12:32.252
have found you a job.

12:32.293 --> 12:33.794
A what?

12:33.836 --> 12:34.837
It'd be with

12:33.836 --> 12:34.837
the Interior Department.

12:34.879 --> 12:36.673
You'd be helping

12:34.879 --> 12:36.673
the environment,

12:36.715 --> 12:37.798
working with people--

12:37.840 --> 12:39.842
you would be making

12:37.840 --> 12:39.842
a real difference.

12:39.884 --> 12:41.802
I can do that.

12:41.844 --> 12:44.639
Thank you, son.

12:44.681 --> 12:46.015
And please, thank that girl

12:46.057 --> 12:48.767
for rocking me in her arms

12:46.057 --> 12:48.767
all night long.

12:58.945 --> 13:00.779
(retching)

13:04.867 --> 13:06.202
All right,

13:04.867 --> 13:06.202
who's ready

13:06.244 --> 13:08.663
for a fantastic

13:06.244 --> 13:08.663
night on the town?

13:08.705 --> 13:09.664
Oh...

13:09.706 --> 13:11.082
Hal, they're beautiful.

13:11.124 --> 13:12.333
Just give me

13:12.375 --> 13:15.295
