This is true.

13:35.064 --> 13:36.232
All right, boys--

13:36.274 --> 13:37.942
your father and I

13:36.274 --> 13:37.942
are leaving now.

13:37.984 --> 13:40.153
I left the number for the

13:37.984 --> 13:40.153
restaurant on the counter.

13:40.194 --> 13:42.280
(retching in other room)

13:40.194 --> 13:42.280
If we get a call,

13:40.194 --> 13:42.280
it better be from the coroner.

13:42.322 --> 13:44.240
(toilet flushing)

13:42.322 --> 13:44.240
Nothing is going to ruin

13:42.322 --> 13:44.240
this night!

13:44.282 --> 13:49.329
M'lady, your

13:44.282 --> 13:49.329
carriage awaits.

13:49.370 --> 13:51.956
(giggling)

13:53.916 --> 13:55.710
Well, I'm out of here.

13:55.752 --> 13:56.919
Back at 10:00?

13:56.961 --> 13:57.878
Sounds good.

13:57.920 --> 13:59.589
Dewey, you and

13:57.920 --> 13:59.589
your dopey dog

13:59.631 --> 14:01.257
are on your own

13:59.631 --> 14:01.257
for an hour or two.

