14:04.803 --> 14:06.513
Oh, he's fine.

14:04.803 --> 14:06.513
He's just busy destroying

14:06.554 --> 14:07.888
your comic book collection.

14:07.930 --> 14:08.847
What?

14:12.560 --> 14:14.103
(snarling)

14:15.021 --> 14:16.690
That's it.

14:16.731 --> 14:18.775
You're getting rid

14:16.731 --> 14:18.775
of that thing right now!

14:18.817 --> 14:20.151
And  you're  going

14:18.817 --> 14:20.151
to pay for this!

14:20.193 --> 14:22.570
I don't think so.

14:20.193 --> 14:22.570
Oh, I

14:20.193 --> 14:22.570
think so.

14:22.612 --> 14:24.572
(barking)

14:24.614 --> 14:25.865
(gasping)

14:26.949 --> 14:28.117
(barking)

14:28.159 --> 14:30.704
Sit!

14:30.745 --> 14:31.912
(growling)

14:31.954 --> 14:33.998
I wasn't talking to him.

14:34.040 --> 14:36.835
(growling continues)

14:44.759 --> 14:46.553
Ever since

14:44.759 --> 14:46.553
the day I was born,

14:46.594 --> 14:49.556
you guys

14:46.594 --> 14:49.556
have been  torturing me.

14:49.597 --> 14:52.726
I remember you trying to switch

14:49.597 --> 14:52.726
me for another baby at the park.

14:52.767 --> 14:55.812
I remember you telling me

14:52.767 --> 14:55.812
the tooth fairy was a vampire.

14:55.854 --> 14:56.937
I remember every

14:56.979 --> 14:59.232
wet Willie,

14:56.979 --> 14:59.232
every booger sandwich,

14:59.273 --> 15:00.817
every stink hat...

15:00.859 --> 15:01.942
Dewey, we're sorry.

15:01.984 --> 15:04.945
...every waffle butt,

15:01.984 --> 15:04.945
every chester backster

15:04.987 --> 15:07.031
and every purple nurple!

15:07.073 --> 15:08.032
And now

15:08.074 --> 15:09.576
you're going to  pay.

15:09.617 --> 15:10.951
(barks)

15:10.993 --> 15:12.829
Dewey, this isn't

15:10.993 --> 15:12.829
going to work.

15:12.871 --> 15:14.038
Mom and Dad will be home

15:12.871 --> 15:14.038
in a few hours,

15:14.080 --> 15:17.124
that dog will be gone,

15:14.080 --> 15:17.124
you'll be in trouble,

15:17.166 --> 15:19.126
and we'll kick your ass

15:17.166 --> 15:19.126
for the next ten years.

15:19.168 --> 15:20.127
I know.

15:20.169 --> 15:21.880
So we'd better get started.

15:21.921 --> 15:23.172
What do you want?

15:24.215 --> 15:25.884
Everything.

15:25.925 --> 15:28.969
I want everything.

15:29.011 --> 15:32.599
Hal, this place

15:29.011 --> 15:32.599
is beautiful.

15:32.640 --> 15:33.474
It's so romantic.

15:33.516 --> 15:35.017
Everything is

15:33.516 --> 15:35.017
fabulous.

15:35.059 --> 15:36.977
Yes, it is fabulous.

15:37.019 --> 15:38.020
Look, they have

15:38.062 --> 15:39.188
your favorite-- oysters!

15:39.230 --> 15:40.607
We'll have to order

15:39.230 --> 15:40.607
some of those.

15:40.648 --> 15:42.483
Actually,

15:40.648 --> 15:42.483
I had a big batch

15:42.525 --> 15:43.984
of oysters for lunch.

15:44.026 --> 15:45.361
You did?

15:45.403 --> 15:46.654
Where did you

15:45.403 --> 15:46.654
get oysters?

15:46.696 --> 15:48.615
A guy has a cart

15:46.696 --> 15:48.615
outside the building.

15:48.656 --> 15:52.410
Besides, I am dying

15:48.656 --> 15:52.410
to try this plain broth--

15:52.452 --> 15:53.703
they're famous for it.

15:53.745 --> 15:54.995
For their broth?

15:53.745 --> 15:54.995
What are you talking about?

15:55.037 --> 15:56.997
Is that your friend Suzy

15:55.037 --> 15:56.997
from work?

15:57.039 --> 15:58.999
Who, that fat old man?

15:59.041 --> 16:02.002
Never mind.

15:59.041 --> 16:02.002
I'm just so excited to be here.

16:02.044 --> 16:03.379
Excuse me, sorry.

16:03.421 --> 16:04.547
Please,

16:04.589 --> 16:05.924
could you turn the air

16:04.589 --> 16:05.924
conditioning like

16:05.965 --> 16:07.007
10-15 degrees colder?

16:07.049 --> 16:09.009
Okay.

16:09.051 --> 16:11.387
Okay...

16:11.429 --> 16:14.098
Hal... what are

16:11.429 --> 16:14.098
you up to?

16:14.140 --> 16:15.683
I'll never tell.

16:15.725 --> 16:16.935
I love this.

16:16.976 --> 16:19.729
I'm having such

16:16.976 --> 16:19.729
a great time.

16:19.771 --> 16:22.273
Me, too.

16:22.315 --> 16:24.734
Excuse me.

16:24.776 --> 16:25.985
Hurry back.

16:27.862 --> 16:30.531
(shuddering)

16:30.573 --> 16:32.199
Excuse me.

16:32.241 --> 16:33.326
I need your help.

16:33.367 --> 16:35.829
Here-- here's $20.

16:35.870 --> 16:38.038
Go and buy me some medicine--

16:35.870 --> 16:38.038
some cold medicine--

16:38.080 --> 16:39.833
and serve it to me

16:38.080 --> 16:39.833
in a champagne glass.

16:39.874 --> 16:42.042
But I-I...

16:39.874 --> 16:42.042
Just stop talking and go!

16:42.084 --> 16:44.044
(moaning)

16:44.086 --> 16:46.172
DEWEY:

16:44.086 --> 16:46.172
Pencils down.

16:47.298 --> 16:50.468
Who wants to read

16:47.298 --> 16:50.468
their essay first?

16:51.719 --> 16:54.013
Marshmallow,

16:51.719 --> 16:54.013
why don't you choose?

16:55.765 --> 16:57.642
(barks)

16:57.684 --> 16:59.519
"50 reasons why Dewey

16:59.560 --> 17:00.561
"is the greatest

16:59.560 --> 17:00.561
brother

17:00.603 --> 17:01.771
"in the history

17:00.603 --> 17:01.771
of the universe

17:01.813 --> 17:03.272
and I'm a worthless

17:01.813 --> 17:03.272
chunk of garbage."

17:03.314 --> 17:05.483
Is that what we were

17:03.314 --> 17:05.483
supposed to be writing about?

17:07.109 --> 17:08.110
From the top.

17:08.152 --> 17:10.738
"50 reasons why Dewey is the

17:08.152 --> 17:10.738
greatest brother in the...

17:10.780 --> 17:11.906
Stop.

17:11.948 --> 17:14.367
Something's not right.

17:16.828 --> 17:18.037
Wait.

17:20.122 --> 17:22.166
There.

17:22.208 --> 17:23.292
Continue.

17:23.334 --> 17:24.377
(doorbell rings)

17:24.418 --> 17:27.087
Nobody move.

17:24.418 --> 17:27.087
(knocking on door)

17:27.129 --> 17:29.465
CRAIG:

17:27.129 --> 17:29.465
Hello?! I know

17:29.507 --> 17:30.717
someone's home.

17:30.758 --> 17:32.886
I saw shapes moving

17:30.758 --> 17:32.886
on the curtain!

17:32.927 --> 17:35.221
Marshmallow, guard.

17:36.556 --> 17:38.599
Hey, sport,

17:36.556 --> 17:38.599
is your dad home?

17:38.641 --> 17:39.976
No, they went to a restaurant,

17:40.018 --> 17:41.936
but they said  you

17:40.018 --> 17:41.936
should go over...

17:41.978 --> 17:43.479
Well, I just came

17:41.978 --> 17:43.479
to drop off some pants.

17:43.521 --> 17:45.147
They got out...

17:43.521 --> 17:45.147
Craig, help!

17:45.189 --> 17:46.566
REESE:

17:45.189 --> 17:46.566
Help up, please!

17:46.607 --> 17:47.567
Dewey's gone crazy.

17:47.608 --> 17:48.526
He's holding us prisoner.

17:48.568 --> 17:50.069
(Marshmallow growls)

17:52.446 --> 17:55.115
I'm sorry you had to see this.

17:55.157 --> 17:57.117
(Marshmallow growls)

17:57.159 --> 17:59.119
Number 12...

17:59.161 --> 18:01.497
his twinkling eyes.

18:01.539 --> 18:02.707
To us.

18:02.749 --> 18:04.000
To us.

18:04.042 --> 18:05.125
You know, Lois...

18:05.167 --> 18:07.336
LOIS (thinking):

18:05.167 --> 18:07.336
Don't pass out.

18:07.378 --> 18:09.129
No! No, keep it together.

18:09.171 --> 18:11.424
Smile, smile! Laugh!

18:11.465 --> 18:13.133
(laughter)

18:13.175 --> 18:15.053
HAL (thinking):

18:13.175 --> 18:15.053
You're going to throw up.

18:15.094 --> 18:17.346
Okay, if it comes to it,

18:15.094 --> 18:17.346
