Think of your favorite Stooge,

18:32.403 --> 18:35.656
and I'll be right back.

18:35.698 --> 18:39.159
Marshmallow, if anyone moves,

18:35.698 --> 18:39.159
eat  them.

18:39.201 --> 18:40.160
This is insane.

18:40.202 --> 18:42.162
We've got to do something.

18:42.204 --> 18:43.163
I'm Moe.

18:43.205 --> 18:44.331
We don't have

18:43.205 --> 18:44.331
a choice.

18:44.373 --> 18:45.959
I say at the

18:44.373 --> 18:45.959
count of three,

18:46.000 --> 18:48.586
we split up and all run

18:46.000 --> 18:48.586
for different doors.

18:48.628 --> 18:50.170
Are you nuts?

18:48.628 --> 18:50.170
He might get one of us.

18:50.212 --> 18:51.464
MALCOLM:

18:50.212 --> 18:51.464
Yeah, but two of us

18:51.505 --> 18:52.882
will get away

18:51.505 --> 18:52.882
and go for help.

18:52.924 --> 18:56.176
I'm willing if you are.

18:52.924 --> 18:56.176
I can't sing anymore.

18:56.218 --> 18:59.179
Ready? On three.

18:59.221 --> 19:00.347
One...

19:00.389 --> 19:01.808
two...

19:01.849 --> 19:03.059
three.

19:03.101 --> 19:04.560
Go, go, go, go, go,

19:03.101 --> 19:04.560
go, go, go, go!

19:04.602 --> 19:05.603
Go, go, go, go!

19:04.602 --> 19:05.603
(barking)

19:05.645 --> 19:07.105
No. Good dog! No, no!

19:07.146 --> 19:09.273
(screaming)

19:07.146 --> 19:09.273
Ah! Ooh! Not the face!

19:09.315 --> 19:11.191
(screaming)

19:11.233 --> 19:12.192
Craig's a good guy.

19:12.234 --> 19:14.028
He always comes

19:12.234 --> 19:14.028
through for us.

19:14.070 --> 19:15.029
I couldn't find

19:15.071 --> 19:16.447
any rusty scissors,

19:15.071 --> 19:16.447
so we're going to have

19:16.489 --> 19:18.407
to use...

19:18.449 --> 19:19.575
Where is he?

19:19.617 --> 19:21.243
He should have

19:19.617 --> 19:21.243
been back by now.

19:21.285 --> 19:22.286
Look at this,

19:21.285 --> 19:22.286
my palms are sweaty.

19:22.328 --> 19:25.164
Would you calm down?

19:22.328 --> 19:25.164
Here he comes.

19:27.541 --> 19:29.293
So?

19:29.335 --> 19:34.007
(slurring):

19:29.335 --> 19:34.007
For some reason, I was fired.

19:34.048 --> 19:37.510
I don't believe it,

19:34.048 --> 19:37.510
he's drunk again.

19:37.551 --> 19:39.512
You're just going to have

19:37.551 --> 19:39.512
to face it, Francis--

19:39.553 --> 19:41.221
there's no hope

19:39.553 --> 19:41.221
for this guy.

19:41.263 --> 19:42.890
The only thing that ever

19:41.263 --> 19:42.890
made him remotely happy

19:42.932 --> 19:46.019
was tormenting

19:42.932 --> 19:46.019
and bullying helpless students.

19:46.060 --> 19:47.728
Without that, he's nothing.

19:49.981 --> 19:53.026
You call that a collage?

19:53.067 --> 19:54.401
Is it an  insult

19:54.443 --> 19:55.862
to the craft.

19:55.903 --> 20:00.116
